WELCOME TO MY ATTEMPT AT RELEARNING BOTH C++ AND GIT!

Rules:
1) a live cell with 0-1, 3+ neighbors die
2) a live cell with 2-3 neighbors stays alive
4) a dead cell with EXACTLY 3 live neighbors becomes alive

Milestones:
1) Data Structures required (Kinda)
2) Pretty print ()
3) Given 1 board state create the next (algorithm implementation) (DONE)
4) Run until given the comman ()
5) Improve the interface ()
6) Create a save state system ()
7) Mess around! ()
8) Work on GIT practices ()

